---
// Section 4 — Methodology
// "How the pipeline gets built." — four steps from brief to hand-off, each paired
// with a line-art glyph that depicts the actual work of that step.
//
// Section id is "how-it-works" — matches HOW_IT_WORKS_ANCHOR in config.ts, so the
// Nav link and Hero secondary CTA resolve here.
---

<section
  id="how-it-works"
  class="py-32 md:py-44 px-6 md:px-10 lg:px-16"
  style="background: var(--color-bg);"
>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section heading + sub-heading -->
    <h2
      data-reveal
      class="font-serif leading-[1.02] tracking-tight max-w-3xl"
      style="
        color: var(--color-ink);
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 5.2vw, 4.25rem);
      "
    >
      How the pipeline gets built.
    </h2>

    <p
      data-reveal
      data-reveal-delay="1"
      class="mt-8 md:mt-10 max-w-2xl text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed"
      style="color: var(--color-ink-muted);"
    >
      Four steps from brief to hand-off.
    </p>

    <!-- Four steps — vertical stack, each step is 2-col on desktop -->
    <div class="mt-20 md:mt-24">
      <!-- Step 01 — Strategy -->
      <div
        data-reveal
        data-reveal-delay="2"
        class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[300px_1fr] gap-8 md:gap-16 py-12 md:py-16 border-t"
        style="border-color: var(--color-rule);"
      >
        <div>
          <!-- Glyph: target/crosshair — strategy = aiming at a defined audience segment -->
          <div class="w-12 h-12" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-full h-full" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="15" />
              <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="9" />
              <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="3" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <line x1="24" y1="4" x2="24" y2="8" />
              <line x1="24" y1="40" x2="24" y2="44" />
              <line x1="4" y1="24" x2="8" y2="24" />
              <line x1="40" y1="24" x2="44" y2="24" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-8 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em]"
            style="color: var(--color-ink-subtle);"
          >
            01
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-2 font-serif"
            style="color: var(--color-ink); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.2vw, 1.875rem);"
          >
            Strategy
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="max-w-xl text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed"
          style="color: var(--color-ink-muted);"
        >
          You tell us your product, your audience, your goals. We translate that
          into pipeline criteria. Which creator archetype, what audience overlap,
          what rate range, what volume cadence. If creator marketing isn't the
          right channel for your goal, we say so before anything moves.
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 02 — Discovery -->
      <div
        data-reveal
        data-reveal-delay="3"
        class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[300px_1fr] gap-8 md:gap-16 py-12 md:py-16 border-t"
        style="border-color: var(--color-rule);"
      >
        <div>
          <!-- Glyph: magnifier scanning a dense field — discovery = our tooling on the creator universe -->
          <div class="w-12 h-12" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-full h-full" aria-hidden="true">
              <!-- background dots visible through/around the lens -->
              <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <circle cx="30" cy="8" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <circle cx="8" cy="24" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <circle cx="38" cy="18" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <circle cx="14" cy="36" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <!-- lens -->
              <circle cx="21" cy="21" r="11" />
              <!-- dots inside lens (highlighted / scanned) -->
              <circle cx="17" cy="18" r="1.2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <circle cx="24" cy="16" r="1.2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <circle cx="25" cy="24" r="1.2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <circle cx="18" cy="25" r="1.2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <!-- handle -->
              <line x1="29" y1="29" x2="40" y2="40" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-8 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em]"
            style="color: var(--color-ink-subtle);"
          >
            02
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-2 font-serif"
            style="color: var(--color-ink); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.2vw, 1.875rem);"
          >
            Discovery
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="max-w-xl text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed"
          style="color: var(--color-ink-muted);"
        >
          Our engine surfaces creators whose audiences align with your brief.
          Candidates are ranked on engagement quality, audience overlap,
          commercial history, and content fit. Not vanity follower counts.
          Every match is reviewed by hand before it reaches you.
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 03 — Package -->
      <div
        data-reveal
        data-reveal-delay="4"
        class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[300px_1fr] gap-8 md:gap-16 py-12 md:py-16 border-t"
        style="border-color: var(--color-rule);"
      >
        <div>
          <!-- Glyph: two speech bubbles — warm-up = first contact, exchange with the creator -->
          <div class="w-12 h-12" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-full h-full" aria-hidden="true">
              <!-- Outgoing bubble (top-left) -->
              <rect x="4" y="8" width="26" height="14" rx="2" />
              <line x1="9" y1="13" x2="25" y2="13" />
              <line x1="9" y1="17" x2="21" y2="17" />
              <polyline points="14 22 12 25 16 22" />
              <!-- Reply bubble (bottom-right) -->
              <rect x="18" y="26" width="26" height="14" rx="2" />
              <line x1="23" y1="31" x2="39" y2="31" />
              <line x1="23" y1="35" x2="35" y2="35" />
              <polyline points="32 26 34 23 30 26" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-8 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em]"
            style="color: var(--color-ink-subtle);"
          >
            03
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-2 font-serif"
            style="color: var(--color-ink); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.2vw, 1.875rem);"
          >
            Warm-up
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="max-w-xl text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed"
          style="color: var(--color-ink-muted);"
        >
          We make first contact. We confirm fit, gauge interest, and qualify a
          working rate ballpark. Cold creators stay off the list. By the time
          it lands, the pipeline is already in motion.
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 04 — Close -->
      <div
        data-reveal
        data-reveal-delay="5"
        class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[300px_1fr] gap-8 md:gap-16 py-12 md:py-16 border-t border-b"
        style="border-color: var(--color-rule);"
      >
        <div>
          <!-- Glyph: stack → arrow → open frame — hand-off = the pipeline transferred to you -->
          <div class="w-12 h-12" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-full h-full" aria-hidden="true">
              <!-- Source: pipeline stack on our side -->
              <rect x="4" y="14" width="14" height="20" rx="1" />
              <rect x="7" y="11" width="14" height="20" rx="1" />
              <!-- Transfer arrow -->
              <line x1="24" y1="22" x2="36" y2="22" />
              <polyline points="32 18 36 22 32 26" />
              <!-- Destination: open receiving frame (you) -->
              <path d="M40 14 L46 14 L46 30 L40 30" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-8 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em]"
            style="color: var(--color-ink-subtle);"
          >
            04
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-2 font-serif"
            style="color: var(--color-ink); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.2vw, 1.875rem);"
          >
            Hand-off
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="max-w-xl text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed"
          style="color: var(--color-ink-muted);"
        >
          You receive the warm pipeline. Each creator with confirmed interest,
          a rate ballpark, and the context you need to brief them. The
          relationship is yours from there.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
